snippet.title: More Super Mario Star World!
snippet.description:
Based off Secret Woods, one of the levels I created which was used in Frauber's hack, "The Missing Stars", and also the first complete new SM64 level ever made. Aside from this, I also made the cave area and (if memory serves correctly) the lava area, which could also see remakes in the future.

SMSW is roughly 80% complete, and it is thanks to the help of others that I have the finances needed to focus on this project. If you're interested in lending a hand and also receiving demos, please check out my Patreon link below.

Funding/Demos: https://www.patreon.com/skelux
Discord: https://skelux.net/forumdisplay.php?fid=18
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BonerLich
Forum: http://skelux.net
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/bonerlich

Edit: For those asking, the project was renamed because too many people were ignoring it while assuming it was just a direct port of Star Road. The new name also makes more sense, given that a 'Star Road' is actually the portal leading to 'Star World' in SMW. This implies SMSR is an incomplete version of my game on the 'road' to creating SMSW.
